sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户/定时任务
    participant Main as main.py
    participant Engine as EvolutionEngine
    participant Buffer as SensoryBuffer
    participant Orchestrator as Orchestrator
    participant EventMonitor as EventMonitor
    participant EventAnalyst as EventAnalyst
    participant SkillWriter as SkillWriter
    participant Pipeline as QualityPipeline
    participant Hippocampus as Hippocampus
    participant Cortex as Cortex
    participant Storage as Storage

    Note over User,Main: 启动入口
    User->>Main: python main.py run-cycle
    activate Main

    Main->>Engine: run_cycle()
    activate Engine

    Note over Engine: 阶段1: OPERATE
    Engine->>Engine: _phase_operate()
    Engine->>Storage: 读取活跃技能
    Storage-->>Engine: skill_list
    Engine->>Buffer: capture(operate_result)

    Note over Engine: 阶段2: DETECT
    Engine->>Orchestrator: delegate("detect", EventMonitor)
    activate Orchestrator
    Orchestrator->>EventMonitor: scan_sessions()
    activate EventMonitor
    EventMonitor->>Storage: 查询最近错误/日志
    Storage-->>EventMonitor: events
    EventMonitor->>EventMonitor: create_report()
    EventMonitor-->>Orchestrator: EventReport
    deactivate EventMonitor
    Orchestrator-->>Engine: detection_result
    deactivate Orchestrator
    Engine->>Buffer: capture(detection_issues)

    Note over Engine: 阶段3: ANALYZE
    Engine->>Orchestrator: delegate("analyze", EventAnalyst)
    activate Orchestrator
    Orchestrator->>EventAnalyst: analyze(detection_issues)
    activate EventAnalyst
    EventAnalyst->>EventAnalyst: analyze_root_cause()
    EventAnalyst->>EventAnalyst: generate_proposal()
    EventAnalyst-->>Orchestrator: AnalysisResult
    deactivate EventAnalyst
    Orchestrator-->>Engine: analysis_result
    deactivate Orchestrator
    Engine->>Buffer: capture(analyses)

    Note over Engine: 阶段4: ENCODE
    Engine->>Orchestrator: delegate("encode", SkillWriter)
    activate Orchestrator
    Orchestrator->>SkillWriter: fill_capability_gap(analysis_result)
    activate SkillWriter
    SkillWriter->>SkillWriter: generate()
    SkillWriter->>Storage: save_skill()
    Storage-->>SkillWriter: skill_id
    SkillWriter-->>Orchestrator: Skill
    deactivate SkillWriter
    Orchestrator-->>Engine: encode_result
    deactivate Orchestrator
    Engine->>Buffer: capture(generated_skills)

    Note over Engine: 阶段5: VERIFY (质量管道)
    Engine->>Pipeline: execute(generated_skills)
    activate Pipeline

    Note over Pipeline: 8阶段管道
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: WRITE阶段
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: TYPECHECK阶段 (mypy)
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: TEST阶段 (pytest)
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: LINT阶段 (flake8)
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: CRITIQUE阶段 (AI评审)
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: REFINE阶段 (如需优化)
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: ESCALATE阶段 (升级判断)
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: ARBITER阶段 (最终仲裁)

    Pipeline-->>Engine: verify_result
    deactivate Pipeline

    Note over Engine: 记忆编码
    Engine->>Buffer: get_all()
    Buffer-->>Engine: all_buffer_data

    Engine->>Hippocampus: encode(all_buffer_data)
    activate Hippocampus
    Hippocampus->>Hippocampus: extract_facts()
    Hippocampus-->>Engine: encoded_facts
    deactivate Hippocampus

    Engine->>Cortex: integrate(encoded_facts)
    activate Cortex
    Cortex->>Cortex: 去重/组织
    Cortex->>Storage: 持久化
    Storage-->>Cortex: memory_id
    Cortex-->>Engine: integrated
    deactivate Cortex

    Engine->>Buffer: clear()

    Engine-->>Main: CycleResult
    deactivate Engine

    Main-->>User: 循环完成输出
    deactivate Main

    Note over User,Main: 定时任务模式 (可选)
    User->>Main: 启动守护进程
    activate Main
    Main->>Engine: 注册定时任务
    Engine->>Engine: schedule(cron="0 2 * * *", callback=run_cycle)
    loop 每日凌晨2点
        CronTrigger->>Engine: 触发
        Engine->>Engine: run_cycle()
    end